>\n留意左好多文日, 我地既文宣其實可以利用唔同地方既文化,<br />\n加以更改, 達成更大效果. 要同全世界We Connect, 要活用唔同地方既文化.<br />\n孤星淚, 係歐美社會一定知道既title, 亦容易勾起佢地既共鳴.<br />\n大家不妨諗諗之後既文宣, 要更加creative.<br />\n勾起其他國家本身既文化共鳴, 先係最佳方法.<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家幫手forward去外國網站或者FB,<br />\n喺澳洲同法國既香港支持者受到大陸人攻擊之下,<br />\n呢張圖就係我地對外文宣既最佳利器.<br />\n當年南斯拉夫內戰, 打左幾年, 國際社會關注但唔出手,<br />\n最後係一張『薩拉熱窩的羅密歐與茱麗葉』既照片成為轉變關鍵.<br />\n羅密歐與茱麗葉既標題, 引起左歐美社會共鳴.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n接下來係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">理念輸出</span></span><br />\n[文宣] 發夢之歌: 自由之旗・自由之民, 一首代表我地理念既歌.<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1476260/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1476260/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Il7Tp2r9qL8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIl7Tp2r9qL8&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1MemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=772fdf0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Il7Tp2r9qL8</a><br />\n<br />\n我地唔單止要宣傳, 仲要有理念. 藉由歌聲追求自由係最好既理念文宣,<br />\n唔會嚇親老一派既香港人, 亦可以觸動到歐美社會既支持.<br />\n我選呢首歌既理由, 同上面講既『薩拉熱窩的羅密歐與茱麗葉』一樣,<br />\n都係能觸動歐美普世價值既issue. 對我地黎講, 一首好歌,<br />\n可以鼓舞士氣, 提醒我地不要放棄.<br />\n<br />\n上面條LINK係我搵既一首歌, 好適合我地用. 大家可以襟上去聽下首歌,<br />\n如果認同既話, 我希望可以搞個萬人齊唱版, 大家可以聽住音樂清唱,<br />\n唱完之後UPLOAD上上面條連登LINK, 我整合之後放出黎.<br />\n<br />\n文宣也好, 歌曲也好, 最重要係做得到be Symbol.<br />\nBatman曾有一段對話:<br />\n&ldquo;People need dramatic examples to shake them out of apathy,<br />\nand I can&rsquo;t do that as Bruce Wayne. As a man I&rsquo;m flesh and blood,<br />\nI can be ignored, I can be destroyed, but as a symbol,<br />\nas a symbol I can be incorruptible. I can be everlasting.&rdquo;<br />\n&mdash; Bruce Wayne (Batman Begins)<br />\n<br />\n我地既文宣同理念, 一定要做到be Symbol, 一聽到某D文宣圖就諗起成個運動,<br />\n一聽到某首歌就能夠代表我地. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">be Symbol, be Symbol, be Symbol</span></span>.<br />\n重要事情講三次.<br />\n<br />\n唯有有左Symbol, 有左令我地寄托夢想既Symbol, 先可以長期落去.<br />\n我地無大台, 唔似印度人有甘地去寄托夢想, 寄托夢想於歌曲就係最好選擇.<br />\n<br />\n818，維園見"},{"pid":"713c067b11ee46a247028e1c4b4177973ddff919","tid":1481541,"uid":128212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649e45d4168178a5e0763b2f4d55f91f28235ea5","tid":1481541,"uid":184433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:41:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"700696311fc2dec49326d08c1a57bb18e1584c22","tid":1481541,"uid":43553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:49:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0ce618635768eb4c1f4476c450f1b959bfd4f77e","tid":1481541,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:51:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fcall-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization%20&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1MemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=cec8a3ae\" target=\"_blank\">http://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization </a><br />\n幫手廣傳出去阿！快d簽啦！<br />\n如果ccp係恐怖組織咁全世界先可以制裁佢咁先會幫到香港 美國佬都出緊力呀 快d配合把ccp定性為恐怖組織！<br />\n對準極權中共⚠️"},{"pid":"f7d8eb5714a7c8682732d03928f3287ae3b9cc7f","tid":1481541,"uid":289693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:58:26.000Z","msg":"好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86669bf015c274ffc1aecb559eff0974fa19f278","tid":1481541,"uid":96169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T20:03:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n良知比分數重要"},{"pid":"37b109d8bf51d14cf29e3ed4be6b5cc5e93565c0","tid